milestones.description: Greenidge has scored 5 hundreds in ODIs, the most for WI breaking Viv Richards's record
Greenidge and Viv Richards's 221-run partnership is the highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 205 between Viv Richards and Haynes
Greenidge and Viv Richards's 221-run partnership is WI's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 205 between Viv Richards and Haynes
Gavaskar and Malhotra's 105-run partnership is IND's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 92 between Amarnath and Yashpal Sharma
Viv Richards has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (98) in an innings in ODIs for WI, going past Viv Richards's 86
Greenidge has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (5) in ODIs for WI, going past Greenidge's 4
This is the highest match aggregate (562) involving teams West Indies & India in ODIs
Greenidge and Viv Richards's 221-run partnership is WI's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 205 between Haynes and Viv Richards
Viv Richards has become the top scorer in ODIs with 2457 runs, going past Greg Chappell's 2331
Greenidge and Viv Richards's 221-run partnership is the highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 205 between Haynes and Viv Richards
Greenidge has broken the record for most sixes (34) in ODIs, going past Lance Cairns's 33
